{
  "stem": "6989.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Came back at night, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If there was, they didn't let children come to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I did not go to any funeral at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't, because it wasn't--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If anything, there was a little more religion in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you know, if I think back now, I remember people coming to the house and they were davening.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know what it was all about though.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was meaningless to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I do remember that on certain occasions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know which occasions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think there we also had, like, two rooms.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it's, it's really a terrible thing, you see.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I feel that my age group is sort of more pathetic, or I don't know what word to use, because I have no memory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have no background.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have no foundation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's like I'm in the air flying around in the air, you know, like--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I just feel that I don't-- I have nothing to ground me down because of that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the questions you're asking, I feel stupid because I just don't know any of the answers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just was completely unaware.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or I, I don't think I blocked it out, because I just don't remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I know that there was very little food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I do have to tell you that this Lena never deserted us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember that they found like one of the plaques from the gate that I told you around the ghetto was sort of a little bit open.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I do remember that she used to push through food for us, and my father would go and get it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yea, from wherever she got it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
